data.description: A beautiful, spacious, bright two-story well-maintained home and a very good investment. Located in an ideal location in Houston, inside the 610 loop, ten minutes from the heart of downtown with great shopping, variety of individual restaurants and the theater. This 2500 square foot home has a living room, dining room, kitchen and kitchen dining area, half/bath and walk-in pantry on first floor. On second floor, a primary bedroom/bath with office adjoining with French doors plus two additional bedrooms with shared bath and a spacious rec room/office and laundry room. Genuine oak hardwood floors downstairs and up with two guest bedrooms carpeted. Two-car garage to front on quiet street, with moderate sized patio garden at back of home. Well populated with potted trees and plants for easy care. Friendly neighbors. Whole Foods, Kroger and HEB nearby. Real estate inside the 610 Loop in River Oaks area has historically held its value regardless of market conditions.
